          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="govuk-body-l">
          Search using an initial only in first name:: TODO ADD IN
          <p class="govuk-body">
            Reason: An exact forename search for names which can be shortened could miss records e.g.
            recorded forenames for Evelyn have included Eve, Eva, Evalyn, Evaline
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="govuk-body-l">
          Shorten the forename by 2 characters and add a wildcard: TODO ADD IN
          <p class="govuk-body">
            Reason: An exact forename search for example for JOHN will miss and records where the forename has been
            incorrectly recorded as JON
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="govuk-body-l">
          Swap surname and forename: TODO ADD IN
          <p class="govuk-body">
            Reason: Where a prisoner has a forename and surname which could be interchangeable - e.g.
            Lewis George/George Lewis - these may have been recorded incorrectly
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="govuk-body-l">
